Interface Jsonschema

All Superinterfaces:
BaseProxy, ValueProxy
public interface Jsonschema
extends ValueProxy

Model definition for Discovery.Jsonschema. This class models an object which will be transmitted to or from the Discovery service.

Author:
Google, Inc.
